* {{ill|UNKNOWN|WD=Q1107286|lt=Futsunushi-no-Mikoto|1=UNKNOWN|WD=Q1107286}}
* {{ill|lt=Himegami|Q22070227|WD=Q22070227|lt=Hime-Ōkami}}

